==English==
===Pronunciation===
*{{AHD|ôrʹdn-əns}}
===Noun===
'''ordinance'''

# a local [[law]] or [[regulation]].
# a religious [[practice]] or [[ritual]] prescribed by the church.

====Usage note====
This word is sometimes confused with [[ordnance]], or military weaponry.

====Translations====
*German: [[Verordnung]] ''f'' (1), [[Ritus]] ''m'' (2)
*Slovak: [[nariadenie]] ''n'' (1)

